    "title": "Industrial Floor Coatings for Automotive Shops & Car Dealerships - Elite South Texas",
    "content": "Automotive\nThe automotive industry has many different flooring needs such as high durability requirements for production and service areas as well as aesthetic value for showrooms. Our easy to maintain surfaces are abrasion resistant and slip resistant even when wet. These protective coatings are resistant to petrochemicals, de-icing salts and other corrosives.\nAdvantages\nImpact and abrasion resistant\nSlip resistant in wet or dry conditions for pedestrian and vehicular safety\nResistant to damage from petrochemicals, de-icing salts and other corrosives\nQuick install options for minimal downtime\nSuitable for high automobile traffic and other heavy machinery\nEasy to clean and maintain\nOptions for line striping, directional arrows and safety markings\nFor new construction and existing surfaces in need of repair and/or protection\nExtreme temperature resistances including freeze/thaw conditions and extreme heat\nCustom colors to match company colors, logos and branding themes\nCove/Cant Base\nService departments\nCar parking decks\nCommercial garages\nAssembly lines and plants\nCar washes & detail shops\nMaintenance shops\nBody shops & painting facilities\nWarehouses\nShowrooms\nCove/Cant Base\nREFLECTOR\nEnhancer\nREFLECTOR\nEnhancer HD\nUrethane Cement",
